+ ./validate -h
validate - Sample application demonstrating validations

Usage:
  validate [command]
  validate [command] --help | -h
  validate --version | -v

Commands:
  calc   Add two numbers
  cat    Show a file

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

